name: Tufin SecureTrack
description: This app supports investigative actions on Tufin SecureTrack
latest_tested_versions: SecureTrack version 16.2 HF2 build 77043, TufinOS Release 2.11 build 891

actions.verbose: This action can also be used to check if the specified IP is blocked by testing the value of the action_result.summary.is_blocked response data path.

example_values: Do not touch ! access to CP !
access-list outside extended permit ip any host 10.10.10.200

actions.description: Check connectivity between source and destination network
actions.verbose:
One of the source_ip or destination_ip parameters need to be specified. If source_ip or destination_ip parameter is not specified, the action will use 'Any'. This action returns a list of all enabled rules, which matches the specified source and destination network. The rules are sorted according to rule order.
Supported protocol:
  • Any
  • TCP
  • UDP
  • ICMP
.

example_values:
ip access-list extended inside
 deny   ip any any
